    <thetext>Follow up from bug 429.

Web-compatible, de-facto results for splice() and splice(0):

js&gt; [1,2,3].splice()
[]
js&gt; [1,2,3].splice(0)
[1,2,3]


But per current spec this returns:

js&gt; [1,2,3].splice()
[1,2,3]
js&gt; [1,2,3].splice(0)
[1,2,3]</thetext>
